  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. If Clothes Catch Fire</h2>
    <p>STOP, DROP, and ROLL on the ground to extinguish flames.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Evacuation Steps</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Know at least two exit routes</li>
      <li>Do not use elevators</li>
      <li>Stay low under smoke</li>
      <li>Follow evacuation signs</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Assembly Point</h2>
    <p>Go directly to the pre-decided meeting spot outside the building.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Do Not Re-enter</h2>
    <p>Never go back inside until authorities declare it safe.</p>
